- Zmije?

536
00:46:47,982 --> 00:46:49,855
U pravu si, Poole.
Ne bi trebalo da si ovde.

537
00:46:49,984 --> 00:46:52,688
Daj mi radio.
Pozvacu Gen. Richardsona.

538
00:46:52,820 --> 00:46:55,192
Siguran sam da ce on moci
da te premesti na drugo mesto.

539
00:46:57,241 --> 00:47:00,408
Gospodo, spremajte veceru,
ovde cemo prenociti.

540
00:47:03,414 --> 00:47:07,708
Kladim se da bi zeleo da imas svoj
srecni zatvarac sada, zar ne, pametnjakovicu?

541
00:47:23,267 --> 00:47:25,390
Sta to radis?

542
00:47:27,813 --> 00:47:30,055
On odlazi kuci uskoro, Linh.

543
00:47:30,191 --> 00:47:32,729
Zeli nam dobru srecu da bi
sigurno stigao na odrediste.

544
00:47:32,860 --> 00:47:35,433
Zelis dobru srecu?

545
00:47:35,571 --> 00:47:38,655
Nemoj mi reci. Imas prastari
Vijetnamski zatvarac od flase...

546
00:47:38,782 --> 00:47:40,692
koji bi mi rado prodao.

547
00:47:40,826 --> 00:47:43,578
Linh ne prodati nista.

548
00:47:43,704 --> 00:47:45,910
Ovde slon donosi dobru srecu.

549
00:47:47,791 --> 00:47:51,457
Ako zelis dobru srecu,
dodirni Bo Tat.

550
00:47:52,796 --> 00:47:55,252
Aha, dobro.

551
00:47:57,843 --> 00:48:00,002
Pa, sta je losa sreca?

552
00:48:00,137 --> 00:48:02,593
Um, ne zvizdi u mraku.

553
00:48:02,723 --> 00:48:04,763
Izaci ce zmije i ujesti te.

554
00:48:04,892 --> 00:48:08,178
- Zmije.
- Moze i gore od toga.

555
00:48:08,312 --> 00:48:12,179
- Aha?
- Ako vidis sovu nocu,

556
00:48:12,316 --> 00:48:14,273
neko u tvojoj porodici umre.

557
00:48:14,401 --> 00:48:16,441
Opa, znaci to je najgore.

558
00:48:16,570 --> 00:48:18,195
- Ne!
- Ne.

559
00:48:18,322 --> 00:48:20,694
Sova nista prema vrani.

560
00:48:20,825 --> 00:48:24,774
Vidis vranu bilo kada,
to veoma losa sreca.

561
00:48:24,912 --> 00:48:26,821
