562
00:48:26,956 --> 00:48:30,870
Kazem ti, ako vidis veliku crnu pticu...

563
00:48:31,001 --> 00:48:32,959
begaj odatle.

564
00:48:37,591 --> 00:48:41,126
Znas to?
Ova zemlja je stvarno prekrasna.

565
00:48:41,262 --> 00:48:43,717
Mislim, sokiran sam.

566
00:48:43,848 --> 00:48:45,223
Aha, to je super, zar ne?

567
00:48:45,349 --> 00:48:47,638
- Malo me podseca na rodni kraj.
