ali nemamo vremena.

588
00:49:53,083 --> 00:49:55,123
Moramo nabaviti kamion,
da li se secas?

589
00:49:55,252 --> 00:49:59,084
Nece dugo trajati. Pored toga,
mozda nam to moze i koristiti.

590
00:50:02,343 --> 00:50:05,344
