623
00:52:53,722 --> 00:52:57,257
Ako se jos malo budes salio
pozvacu znas-ti-koga.

624
00:52:59,448 --> 00:53:02,055
Treba nam hrana za slona.

625
00:53:03,941 --> 00:53:06,776
Hej! Stop!

626
00:53:06,902 --> 00:53:08,811
Bo Tat mora da ide.

627
00:53:08,946 --> 00:53:12,030
Hrana! Voda!

628
00:53:12,158 --> 00:53:14,067
